{"tid":2510279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：向心在台灣否認洗黑錢　指控罪侮辱香港金融監管體系","createTime":"2021-04-30T05:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T05:38:24.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d50bd59c7f5608cd3cf4dcc51335adc6e4d4dd0c","tid":2510279,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台北地方法院首度開庭，處理本港商人向心和妻子被指控違反洗錢防制法，兩人否認犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n向心指出，他在香港資本市場從事巨額交易將近30年，公開透明，受監管嚴格；<strong>檢察官說他做虛假交易，不僅是對他個人極大侮辱，也是對香港金融監管體系的極大侮辱</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n向心強調不是共諜，更不是洗黑錢罪犯，一生從無犯罪，甚至連交通違規都沒有。起訴書所說的犯罪，完全不是事實。<br />\n<br />\n辯護律師表示，向心在香港及大陸未有被起訴及調查洗黑錢，甚至檢方指他非法集資後，向心立即向香港證監會舉報並配合調查，<strong>證監會指出向心並不是非法集資的共犯，向心也獲得香港警務處發出的無犯罪紀錄證明</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n向心和妻子被指控與中國國太公司合作，將詐騙所得隱匿至香港，再將約3億元新台幣匯進台灣的銀行購買豪宅，被當局在本月初起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588587-20210430.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588587-20210430.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT4lS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=860f6ac5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588587-20210430.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=83bc0825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588587-20210430.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"51ac93b0be9979df9f43eef64cf0e3ea48de42b4","tid":2510279,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"向華強啲子子孫孫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f6b816d5e5b1deb852caafcb65ab31832882fd","tid":2510279,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28362f5c2c7c7826024da2b1b4dadaa7f60c3ae4","tid":2510279,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"向前後左中右上下<br />\n向心肝脾肺腎"}]}